New User for Clearing Firm "551" and Exchange "CBOE" !

Product Creation Test Plan (Copy) Fixed: Test Case 1:Market Maker creates new equity FLEX fixed strategy product Using Create New Product window with auction type as FLEX
Test Case 2:Broker Dealer creates new equity FLEX fixed strategy product Using Create New Product window with auction type as FLEX
Test Case 3:Market Maker creates new index FLEX fixed strategy product Using Create New Product window with auction type as FLEX
Test Case 4:Broker Dealer creates new index FLEX fixed strategy product Using Create New Product window with auction type as FLEX
Test Case 5:Market Maker creates New FLEX Product using FLEX Auction Window
Test Case 6:Verify that Buy Write Strategy is created For Fixed Products
Test Case 7:Verify Product is rejected if Price type is percentage and Buy Write Check box is checked
Test Case 8:Verify that a FLEX product with more than 15 years of expiration cannot be created
Test Case 9:Verify that a FLEX product with less than 15 years of expiration can be created
Test Case 10:Verify that a FLEX product with equal to 15 years of expiration can be created
Test Case 11:Verify that flex Strategy Product created if ratio of Option leg to Stock Leg is less than 8:100
Test Case 12:Verify that flex Strategy Product created if ratio Option leg to Stock Leg is equal to 8:100
Test Case 13:Verify that flex Strategy Product rejected if ratio of Option leg to Stock Leg is more than 8:100
Test Case 14:Verify that flex Strategy Product is rejected if Ratio of largest option to smallest option leg is greater than 3:1
Test Case 15:Verify that flex Strategy Product created if Ratio of largest option to smallest option leg is equal to 3:1
Test Case 16:Verify that flex Strategy Product created if Ratio of largest option to smallest option leg is less than 3:1
Test Case 17:Verify that flex Strategy Product created for 8 legs if Ratio of largest option to smallest option leg is less than 3:1
Test Case 18:Verify that a fixed FLEX strategy product cannot have two legs with same information
Test Case 19:Verify that flex Strategy Product cannot have more than one Equity leg
Test Case 20:Verify that Flex allows Strategies up to Eight legs
Test Case 21:Verify fixed strategy product cannot be created with 9 legs
Test Case 22:Verify that 8 Leg Buy Write Fixed Strategy is created For Fixed Products
Test Case 23:Verify that 9 Leg Buy Write Fixed Strategy is cannot be created For Fixed Products
Test Case 24:Verify that a FLEX buy write strategy with ratio of option leg to stock leg as 1:100 can be created
Test Case 25:Verify that a FLEX buy write strategy with ratio of option leg to stock leg not equal to 1:100 cannot be created (stock leg ratio less than 100)
Test Case 26:Verify that a FLEX buy write strategy with ratio of option leg to stock leg not equal to 1:100 cannot be created (stock leg ratio greater than 100)
Test Case 27:Verify that flex Strategy Product cannot be created without ratio
Test Case 28:Verify that a new product can be created using Copy existing product
Copy functionality is specific to the GUI CANNOT BE AUTOMATED. Verify Manually
Test Case 29:Verify that Fixed Equity Strategy product cannot be created withAM Settlement Type
Not applicable for Automation Testing. Verify Manually
Test Case 30:Verify that FLEX strategy product creation will be rejected if one of the legs matches with an existing standard product
Test Case 31:Verify that FLEX strategy product creation will be rejected if one of the legs matches with an existing inactive FLEX product
Test Case 32:Verify that new product will be routed to existing FLEX product if it already exists
Test Case 33:Verify that the FLEX series becomes restricted if one of its legs becomes restricted
